---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="FraiseQL for Developers - Quick Start & Documentation"
  description="Get started with FraiseQL as a developer: SDKs, schema authoring, development workflow, and common patterns."
>
  <div style="padding: 2rem; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1>FraiseQL for Developers</h1>
    <p>
      Schema authoring in Python/TypeScript, SDKs for 16+ languages, fast
      development workflow.
    </p>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Quick Start (5 minutes)</h2>
      <p>Get a working GraphQL API up and running:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Install: npm install fraiseql-cli</li>
        <li>Create schema: Create schema.json with your types</li>
        <li>Compile: fraiseql compile schema.json</li>
        <li>Run: fraiseql server --schema schema.compiled.json</li>
        <li>Query: Send GraphQL queries to localhost:8080</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Supported Languages & SDKs</h2>
      <p>Official SDKs available for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Python</li>
        <li>TypeScript/JavaScript</li>
        <li>Rust</li>
        <li>Go</li>
        <li>Java</li>
        <li>C#/.NET</li>
        <li>PHP</li>
        <li>Ruby</li>
        <li>Swift</li>
        <li>Kotlin</li>
        <li>R</li>
        <li>Scala</li>
        <li>Elixir</li>
        <li>Haskell</li>
        <li>Clojure</li>
        <li>Lua</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Schema Authoring Patterns</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Type definitions with decorators</li>
        <li>Query definitions</li>
        <li>Mutation definitions</li>
        <li>Field-level permissions</li>
        <li>Pagination patterns</li>
        <li>Filtering & sorting</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Development Workflow</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Watch mode: fraiseql watch</li>
        <li>Hot reloading on schema changes</li>
        <li>Test data generation with fraiseql-seed</li>
        <li>Database migrations with confiture</li>
        <li>Local development database setup</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h2>Common Patterns</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Nested queries</li>
        <li>Aggregate queries</li>
        <li>Multi-tenant queries</li>
        <li>Complex mutations</li>
        <li>Role-based access control</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
